abstract: Sen Tim Kaine, Democrat of Virginia, will announce that he is joining Ready for Hillary, super PAC trying to build grass-roots support for potential presidential run by Hillary Rodham Clinton in 2016.
lead_paragraph: Senator Tim Kaine is the latest Democrat to endorse Hillary Rodham Clinton for president, even though she has not said whether she will run.

headline.main: Virginia Senator Pledges Support for Clinton in 2016
